curam.util.client.domain.convert.ClientDomainConverter, DomainConverter, DomainPlugIn, PlugIn
public class InternalIDConverter
extends SvrInt64BareConverter

Converter for the INTERNAL_ID domain. As these values are not displayed on the pages and are used mostly as parameter values, the formatter does not use a thousands separator character. Otherwise, this is identical to the converter for SVR_INT64.
